The paper proposes a distributed algorithm for solving a constrained convex optimization problem over a network of clustered agents. The problem involves communication and computation resource management, and the algorithm is linked to the augmented Lagrangian approach. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
